We heard your feedback and realized that we need to be more versatile for you.

So we are moving to the new pricing model that will allow you to pick any desired plugin separate and not the whole system as before.

We are sure that this turn around will have only positive changes on user engagement as Publishers know their users and now will be able to deliver the best solution for them.

New pricing will be applied to all new clients.

We will convert existing clients to it as well in individual manner.





|   Page views    |    <1m    |   1-4m    |   4-10m   |                  > 10m                  |
| :-------------: | :-------: | :-------: | :-------: | :-------------------------------------: |
|  Emote widget   | $10/month | $30/month | $70/month | [Contact us](mailto:support@vuukle.com) |
| Powerbar widget |   Free    | $10/month | $25/month | [Contact us](mailto:support@vuukle.com) |
| Comments widget | $9/month  | $49/month | $99/month | [Contact us](mailto:support@vuukle.com) |

*10% discount if paid annually.

